channel.title: Comments on: Birchbox July 2013 Review and Photos

item.title: By: Sarah Cosper
item.dc:creator: Sarah Cosper
item.description:
In reply to <a href="/birchbox-july-2013-review-and-photos/#comment-349">Suzi</a>.
Other people were saying they got the same polish from the month before too! I'd like to get a different brand, for sure.

item.title: By: Suzi
item.dc:creator: Suzi
item.description:
I seriously can't believe they're still sending out that polish...I got a bottle months ago when I was still signed up for Birchbox. And it's still sitting unopened. Way too "shrinking violet" for my fabulous talons.
I like the way you think though...a Birchbox/Burn Notice team-up would definitely get me to resubscribe! I'd want Fiona to do the picking though, girl's got style. Maybe some Hawaiian print hair ties in honor of Sam? Perfume that's really knockout gas? C'mon Birchbox, give the people what they want! ;)
